works.description:
"If you are new to site design, or an  
experienced pro, this theme will do what you need. You don’t need to know a  
stitch of code, and it works just as advertised.
Pagelines is a premium WordPress theme design company. Their offering has  
been just 4 unique themes – each with a free and a pay version. This pales  
in comparison to the 20, 40 or 100 themes that some designers offer for the  
WordPress platform."

"o be honest, as a user of pagelines premium wordpress themes, when I  
installed the theme at the first time I was overwhelmed. I had never seen  
so many options in a theme before. You can literally change everything –  
and true to their promise – without needing to know any code."
